CakePhp 2.x Plugin for creating dynamic pages in cake with custom content

Setup:
1. Import dynamic_pages.sql in Config/Schema/

2. Add the following line to your app/Config/bootstrap.php
    CakePlugin::load('DynamicPages', array('routes' => true));

3. Use /admin/pages to manage pages

4. Style pages with your site css. The following structure is  the default view.
<div class="pages view">
    <h2 class="title">...</h2>
    <p class="copy">...</p>
</div>
